Channel Hellfire		KEY:Diabolist ~ Channel Hellfire	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary				DEFINE:DiabolistChannelHellfireTimes|0																					DESC:You can alter spells that deal energy damage to instead deal hellfire damage. You can do this as a free action %1 times per day. Spells altered to use hellfire gain the lawful and evil descriptors.|DiabolistChannelHellfireTimes																										BONUS:VAR|DiabolistChannelHellfireTimes|max(1,CHA)																							SOURCEPAGE:p.45	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DiabolistChannelHellfireTimes
Infernal Bargain		KEY:Diabolist ~ Infernal Bargain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																															DESC:If you make use of Planar Ally (or a similar spell), you can make an opposed Charisma check against a called (but not summoned) devil. If you succeed, the devil reduces the price it demands to serve by half.																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.45
Heresy			KEY:Diabolist ~ Heresy			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary				DEFINE:DiabolistHeresyLVL|0	DEFINE:DiabolistHeresyBonus|0																		DESC:You gain a +%1 bonus on all checks made to research specific devils' true names or sigils.|DiabolistHeresyBonus																																													BONUS:VAR|DiabolistHeresyBonus|floor((DiabolistHeresyLVL+3)/6)*2																					SOURCEPAGE:p.45
Hellish Soul		KEY:Diabolist ~ Hellish Soul		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																															DESC:You have been deemed useful enough to the cause of Hell to be allowed a brief respite from damnation. If killed by any means outside of the will of Asmodeus, the archdevils, or another influential force in Hell, you can be resurrected as normal.																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.45
Infernal Transport	KEY:Diabolist ~ Infernal Transport	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike					DEFINE:DiabolistInfernalTransportTimes|0																					DESC:You can transport yourself through Hell in a burst of brimstone. You may use this ability twice per day as per Dimension Door, or expend both uses to travel as if using Teleport. You cannot use this ability to enter or leave areas warded against evil creatures.																				BONUS:VAR|DiabolistInfernalTransportTimes|2																								SOURCEPAGE:p.45	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per day	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|DiabolistInfernalTransportTimes
Hellfire Ray		KEY:Diabolist ~ Hellfire Ray		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.SpellLike					DEFINE:DiabolistHellFireRayLVL|0									SPELLS:Class|TIMES=2|CASTERLEVEL=DiabolistHellFireRayLVL|Hellfire Ray,16+CHA	DESC:You may use Hellfire Ray twice per day.
Master Conjurer		KEY:Diabolist ~ Master Conjurer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																															DESC:When you call a devil whose name you know, you may cast the calling spell as a standard action and bargain with it as a move action. You add half your Bluff, Diplomacy, or Intimidate modifier on the bargaining Charisma check (if any).

